org.sql: SELECT DISTINCT users.* FROM users INNER JOIN email_addresses ON email_addresses.user_id = users.id WHERE users.type IN ('User', 'AnonymousUser') AND LOWER(email_addresses.address) IN ('foo@example.org') ORDER BY users.id ASC LIMIT "$1"
